Package com.flipkart.DAO

Interface GymOwnerInterfaceDAO

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GymOwnerDAO
    public interface GymOwnerInterfaceDAO
    This interface defines the data access operations related to Gym Owner functionality. It includes methods for retrieving gym owner lists, registering new gym owners, managing approval status, and handling approval requests.
